{"tid":2093864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外國記者有冇報導 冇字連儂牆，數字榮光同圖案光時？","createTime":"2020-07-04T07:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T03:38:13.000Z","uid":272805,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4483ff140ae455728099ce0ecc6d6d939bea021f","tid":2093864,"uid":272805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T07:08:46.000Z","msg":"討論規避定係照叫係冇問題<br />\n我反而想知外國朋友知唔知香港發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n世界各地都有國家安全法例<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">但法國人唱Do You Hear the People Sing會不會變數字歌？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n「光時」又點解變到好似哈利波特入面「佛地魔」咁唔講得？<br />\n<br />\n外國記者朋友應該要報導下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但記得要留意國安法或者提醒國民唔好犯國安法<br />\n萬一唔小心嚟到香港就俾人拉咗就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d4342a4abb794511397657a50fa3c46538744ea","tid":2093864,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-07T03:38:13.000Z","msg":"推"}]}